Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你在把我当盾牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会给你加血的啦 所以再为我献身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个房间…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副本区域中存在5-10只特殊怪物——RaidBoss
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(326,670)}RaidZone
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一监狱的邦迪弥耶 怎么看都是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海洛斯的九大监狱啊 真怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:41.20,Warning,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(450,450)\fs28}注：*在第十个资料片「梦幻的心脏」中实装的团队副本海洛斯的九大监狱 开始只能攻打第一~第八监狱 攻略顺序自由 全部通关后可以开启第九监狱 根据监狱的通关顺序会影响后期副本的难度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那时候的RaidBoss吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:46.36,Status,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(152,72)\fad(150,200)}布里甘提亚第一庭院的邦迪弥耶 Lv.91
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:46.36,Status,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(130,201)\fad(150,200)}Rank/Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物模型的重复使用还是挺常见的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸位 它要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家散开 准备战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.34,0:05:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一队攻击右脚正面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二队攻击左脚侧面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三队到左后方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四队右后方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摆好阵型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,束缚吼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}AnchorhHowl
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先按照通常套路去磨血
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给输出职业加上攻击力增加和追加伤害的buff
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后卫则从安全范围进行远距离攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要给作为坦克的战士提供大量回复
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和降低伤害或增加防御力的支援
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后最重要的是仇恨管理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说将敌人的注意力保持在坦克身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}这个大鸟怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想飞起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是某种攻击的发动前兆？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城惠先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无视仇恨的范围攻击？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚惠 损伤报告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移动阻碍5
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石化4
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:06:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即死1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点帮我回复
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复活就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是清buff时没有的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快上DEBUFF
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 迪米卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢吞吞的回复谁等的了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎啸拳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}TigerEchoFist
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十字斩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}CrossSlash
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂快看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算打掉了十分之一了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那一波又有几个人倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个跳到下面了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个从区域中消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.47,0:07:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 向上面移动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会喷火的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RAID BOSS的攻击会随着HP的减少会变得强力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放技能时机和属性都和之前不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得下流了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要想对付必须采取与通常的战斗不同的战术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.51,0:08:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直继 特托拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是聚集强大的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是无法到达胜利的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪特隆石化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 坦克全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有没有治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有了 全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威廉 这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反复进行灭团或撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探索对手的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将其突破
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反复进行了和第一庭院的邦迪弥耶的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:09:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没全灭过 但不断忍受和那相差无几的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又失误了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让身体记住模式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行分析试了多种攻略方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团队副本就是根据对象不同可进行一个月以上的长期战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(227,670)}Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是转眼即逝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后会使用无视仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随机使十人状态异常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者使用让人即死的那个技能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下次战斗时计算一下间隔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,60秒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,间隔是60秒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,计算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1003,710)}1 2 3 4…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绕到背后去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快上DEBUFF
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请快一点站好位置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1003,710)}5 6 7…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RAID BOSS的技能有冷却时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能将其把握好 进行回避
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将伤害降到最小的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,60
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威廉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:09:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我这招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发光的技能没放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好诶 把技能打断了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气打掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加大DPS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将敌人的每个长处和短都记住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,且稳定好团队配合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就是时间的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将RAID BOSS打败后可以获得幻想级的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着是第二只RAID BOSS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.97,0:10:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣之庭院的爱尔莱茵达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是会狂刷清仇恨和召唤守护兽的难敌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在十几回的挑战之后将其战胜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:11:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样将RAID BOSS一个个打败 前往通关
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是FULL RAID
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从首杀副本开始后已经过了三星期
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(501,670)}Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我去死怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说了到下一回合之前等一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米迪米的仇恨值…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少啰嗦祭不倒翁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米迪米后面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞龙腿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}WyvernKick
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治疗流程都被打乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只能进行援护了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越深入越能切实感受到这个副本的难易度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物的等级提升 被迫陷入苦战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说攻略状况了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连区域的全貌都没抓到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不小心爱上我 那就对不起咯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了赶紧点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 那么我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回应大家的请求~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极光女神之治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}Aurora Heal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中火力攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避开近战攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自打倒了最初的两只BOSS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一直没能继续碰到RaidBOSS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷宫的探索也止步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗陷入了胶着状态
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.37,0:12:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为还有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.27,0:12:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指副本BOSS的数量吗
